      {
        "type": "h2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Cost Analysis and Scaling Considerations"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Pricing for Nanonets OCR S is usage-based, at $0.50 per 1,000 images for the standard tier, with volume discounts available. This includes API calls, model inference, and basic support. For high-throughput scenarios, consider the enterprise plan, which offers dedicated instances and SLAs for latency guarantees. Self-hosting the F16 model is an option for air-gapped environments, but requires GPU infrastructure and maintenance overhead."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "To optimize costs, implement caching for repeated images and use batch endpoints to reduce API call frequency. Monitor usage via the dashboard to set alerts for unexpected spikes. Compared to alternatives, Nanonets OCR S provides a middle ground: cheaper than cloud-based services like Google Vision for moderate volumes, but with better accuracy than self-hosted open-source tools."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "ul",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "lic",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Standard tier",
                    "bold": true
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ": $0.50 per 1,000 images, ideal for startups and mid-sized teams."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "lic",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Enterprise tier",
                    "bold": true
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ": Custom pricing with volume discounts, includes priority support."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "lic",
